"         <span class=\"medCalcFontFormuli\">",
"          RiskFactors = (ln(Age) * 3.06117) + (ln(TotalChol) * 1.12370) - (ln(HDLChol) * 0.93263) +  (ln(SysBP) * SysBPFactor) + Cig + DM - 23.9802",
